headline: Wall Street Analysts Have Consensus Hold Recommendation For Baxter International Inc. (BAX)
summary: Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX) is among the Top 15 Lowest P/E Ratios of the S&P 500 in 2025. On December 2, Morgan Stanley analyst Patrick Wood cut his price target on the stock to $15 from $19 while keeping an Underweight rating.
